The Shift-Tab FvwmForm short cut does not work on my
machine. A test like this fails:

if (ks == XK_Tab && (event.xkey.state & ShiftMask))

as Shift-Tab generate the keysym "XK_ISO_Left_Tab"
here.

Maybe a solution is to do something like that to find the
Shift-Tab keysym:

KeyCode tab = XKeysymToKeycode(dpy, XK_Tab);
shift_tab_ks = XKeycodeToKeysym(dpy, tab, ShiftMask);

I use this method in FvwmScript.

